news.title: Gujarat: Ordinance to amend land-grabbing laws issued
news.para: The Gujarat Land Grabbing (Prohibition) (Amendment) Ordinance, 2022 has modified the original provisions of the Act which were affecting tribal rights.

news.title: Patna: 19 held in crackdown on illegal sand mining at Mekra village
news.para: According to sources, the team conducted a raid and apprehended the smugglers while they were transporting white sand in two large boats.

news.title: CCI directs probe into alleged abuse of dominant position by Chandigarh housing board
news.para: CHB appears to have relieved itself by not making time as an essence for fulfilling its obligations towards the allottee, the Competition Commission of India (CCI) said.
